{"parentUuid":"03b519a6-5608-4ea9-b3ff-4a3bafd04348","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a85079ae82257d010","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CcskcPJ52vEeMfi1ZJvMK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013CBu3TfPCVQxHSkpYZZV6E","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\docs\\system_architecture.md","old_string":"Split-token API keys (`mtr_live_<key_id>_<secret>`), Argon2id-hashed at rest.\nAn in-process, TTL-bounded verification cache (keyed on the public `key_id`,\nguarded by a constant-time digest comparison) avoids paying the Argon2id cost\non every request while the durable store stays Argon2id-only. See","new_string":"Split-token API keys (`mtr_live_<key_id>_<secret>`), Argon2id-hashed at rest.\nClients present the key in the standard bearer scheme —\n`Authorization: Bearer mtr_live_<key_id>_<secret>` — which is also the auth\ncontext a DAST job (ZAP/Schemathesis) reads to authenticate its scan (DAST-3).\nAn in-process, TTL-bounded verification cache (keyed on the public `key_id`,\nguarded by a constant-time digest comparison) avoids paying the Argon2id cost\non every request while the durable store stays Argon2id-only. See"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":614,"cache_read_input_tokens":108726,"output_tokens":1055,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":614},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":1055,"cache_read_input_tokens":108726,"cache_creation_input_tokens":614,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":614,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcskcMrWGadGjnWUxUi3G